snippet.title: 悪魔の悪夢 / 2018_05_10 / REV.B0010
snippet.description:
some footage of the faux-lighting i've been working on as well as more of this stage - including an extreme example of the fact that lives in this game are both a kind of score as well as "hit points" - you should try to get a lot.

this is footage of a work in progress still in its "early" stages of development.
